### Home Page Components (`/app/page.tsx`)
- **[NEW] Hero Section:** Immersive headline ("The fastest way to launch your startup", "Live with us in Leuven"), dynamic stats counter, magnetic primary CTA button.
- **[NEW] Value Proposition Grid:** Sleek bento-box or grid style cards for "A Residency for Builders", "Ship tonight", "Real feedback", and "Momentum".
- **[NEW] Testimonials (Social Proof):** Animated marquee or minimalist cards for quotes from past participants.
- **[NEW] Perks Section:** Highlighting Mentorship, Lovable credits, and free fuel with elegant iconography.
- **[NEW] FAQ Accordion:** Smooth expanding/collapsing questions.
- **[NEW] Footer:** Minimalist footer with links and social icons.

## Verification Plan
### Automated Tests
- Run `npm run build` to ensure the Next.js application compiles successfully without type or linting errors.

### Manual Verification
- Run `npm run dev` and navigate to `http://localhost:3000` via the browser subagent.
- Visually inspect the hero section, scrolling animations, and responsive behavior across mobile and desktop viewport sizes.
- Verify that dark mode colors and high-contrast typography meet the premium aesthetic requirements.
